---
title: About
layout: 'base.njk'
eleventyExcludeFromCollections: true
---

<main>

  <!-- About Hero (Personal / Sales) -->
  <section class="about-hero">  
    <div class="about-hero-container container">
      <div class="about-hero-content">
        <p class="about-hero-title">
          Staff engineer, frontend systems, builder/tinkerer.
        </p>
        <p class="about-hero-lead">
          I help products go from <span class="rainbow">0 → 1</span> to <span class="rainbow">1 → 100</span>.
        </p>
        <p style="margin: 0 0 20px; line-height: 1.5; font-weight: 300;">
          I specialise in frontend systems and product engineering — taking ideas from sketch to reliable,
          scalable experiences. I've built both developer-facing products (SDKs, tools, and platforms) and
          B2B SaaS platforms with customer-facing interfaces used by thousands of teams. I care about
          the whole journey: discovery, first ship, and the unglamorous scaling work that comes after.
        </p>
        <div style="margin-top: 10px;">
          <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/singhkunal2050" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary">Let's Work Together</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="about-hero-image">
        {# Static image on load, swapped to a GIF on hover via JS #}
        <img
          src="{{ '/img/kunal/photo.png' | url }}"
          data-static-src="{{ '/img/kunal/photo.png' | url }}"
          data-hover-src="{{ 'https://media.tenor.com/rMxNr07CxSMAAAAM/cat-crazy-cat.gif  ' | url }}"
          alt="Kunal Singh | singhkunal2050">
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Career Journey -->
  <section class="about-journey">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="head_text" style="text-align: center; padding-bottom: 30px;">
        Career <span class="rainbow head_text">Journey</span>
      </h2>

      <div class="about-journey-list">
        {%- for experience in collections.experience | reverse -%}
        <article class="about-journey-item">
          <div class="about-journey-card">
            <img src="{{ experience.data.logo | url }}" alt="{{ experience.data.company }} logo" class="about-journey-logo">
            <h3 class="subhead_text">{{ experience.data.title }}</h3>
            <p><strong>{{ experience.data.company }} · {{ experience.data | formatDateRange }} · {{ experience.data.location }}{% if experience.data.work_type %} ({{ experience.data.work_type }}){% endif %}</strong></p>
            {% if experience.data.description %}
            <p style="margin: 8px 0 12px;">
              {{ experience.data.description }}
            </p>
            {% endif %}
            {% if experience.data.achievements %}
            <ul>
              {%- for achievement in experience.data.achievements -%}
              <li>{{ achievement }}</li>
              {%- endfor -%}
            </ul>
            {% endif %}
          </div>
        </article>
        {%- endfor -%}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Life Snapshots Gallery -->
  <section class="about-life">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="head_text" style="text-align: center; padding-bottom: 30px;">
        Life <span class="rainbow head_text">Snapshots</span>
      </h2>

      <div class="about-life-board">
        {%- for snapshot in collections["life-snapshots"] | sortByOrder -%}
        <article class="about-life-card">
          <div class="about-life-pin">
            <span class="about-life-pin-head"></span>
            <figure>
              <img src="{{ snapshot.data.image | url }}" alt="{{ snapshot.data.caption }}">
              <figcaption>{{ snapshot.data.caption }}</figcaption>
            </figure>
            <p>
              {{ snapshot.data.description }}
            </p>
          </div>
        </article>
        {%- endfor -%}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- Beyond the Code -->
  <section class="about-beyond-code">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="head_text" style="text-align: center; padding-bottom: 30px;">
        Beyond the <span class="rainbow head_text">Code</span>
      </h2>
      <p style="max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto 10px;">
        Outside of work, I enjoy experimenting with side projects, writing about engineering,
        and speaking at meetups. I like taking things I’ve learned in real projects and
        turning them into talks, blog posts, or tools that others can pick up quickly.
      </p>
      <p style="max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto;">
        You’ll often find me tinkering with new frameworks, improving my dev environment,
        or helping friends and peers debug their apps and workflows.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Closing CTA -->
  <section class="about-cta">
    <div class="container" style="text-align: center; padding: 40px 0;">
      <h2 class="head_text" style="margin-bottom: 10px;">
        Interested in <span class="rainbow head_text">working together</span>?
      </h2>
      <p style="max-width: 640px; margin: 0 auto 20px;">
        If you’re building developer tools, SaaS products, or customer‑facing web experiences
        and need someone who can own both the frontend and the delivery pipeline,
        I’d love to chat.
      </p>
      <div>
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/singhkunal2050" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary">
          Say hi on LinkedIn
        </a>
        <a href="mailto:singhkunal2050@gmail.com" class="btn btn-outline">
          Email me
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</main>
